hover:bg-gray-100\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us <svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 ml-2\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\"></path><path d=\"M17 7l-10 10\"></path><path d=\"M8 7l9 0l0 9\"></path></svg></a></div></div><main class=\"container py-10 space-y-8\"><header class=\"space-y-2\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Wardrobe Maker</h1><p class=\"max-w-3xl text-gray-600\">Build a quick rough estimate with a lane-based structure: enter measurements, tweak shelf/drawer setup, and instantly preview a minimal visual wardrobe front.</p></header><section class=\"grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]\"><div class=\"p-5 border rounded-xl bg-zinc-50 space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Project Setup</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2\"><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Project name<input class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" placeholder=\"Master bedroom wardrobe\" value=\"My Wardrobe\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Available wall width (inches)<input type=\"number\" min=\"1\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"144\"/></label></div><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Notes<textarea rows=\"3\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" placeholder=\"Color palette options can be attached later.\"></textarea></label><div class=\"grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"p-3 border rounded-md bg-white\"><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Total lane width</p><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">90 in</p></div><div class=\"p-3 border rounded-md bg-white\"><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Wall usage</p><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">63%</p></div><div class=\"p-3 border rounded-md bg-white\"><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Front area</p><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">52.5 sq ft</p></div><div class=\"p-3 border rounded-md bg-white\"><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">Volume</p><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">105.0 cu ft</p></div></div><div class=\"p-3 text-sm border rounded-md bg-white\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Material index:</span> <!-- -->137<p class=\"mt-1 text-gray-500\">Rough only: higher index means larger build and likely higher cost.</p></div></div><div class=\"p-5 border rounded-xl bg-zinc-50 space-y-3\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Lane Controls</h2><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-black rounded-md\">Add lane</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-md bg-black text-white border-black\">Lane 1</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-md bg-white\">Lane 2</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-md bg-white\">Lane 3</button></div><div class=\"grid gap-3 pt-2\"><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Lane label<input class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"Lane 1\"/></label><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\"><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Width (in)<input type=\"number\" min=\"12\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"30\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Height (in)<input type=\"number\" min=\"60\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"84\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Depth (in)<input type=\"number\" min=\"12\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"24\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Ground gap (in)<input type=\"number\" min=\"0\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"0\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Shelves<input type=\"number\" min=\"0\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"4\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Drawers<input type=\"number\" min=\"0\" class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\" value=\"2\"/></label></div><label class=\"grid gap-1 text-sm\">Door style<select class=\"px-3 py-2 border rounded-md\"><option value=\"open\">Open</option><option value=\"single\">Single door</option><option value=\"double\" selected=\"\">Double door</option><option value=\"sliding\">Sliding</option></select></label><button type=\"button\" class=\"self-start px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-md hover:bg-red-50\">Remove selected lane</button></div></div></section><section class=\"p-5 border rounded-xl bg-zinc-50 space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Visual Lane Preview</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">This front elevation uses lane widths and heights for a simple realistic visual feel.</p><div class=\"p-4 overflow-x-auto bg-white border rounded-lg\"><div class=\"min-w-[700px]\"><div class=\"flex items-end gap-1 h-[360px] bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-50 to-zinc-100 p-2 border rounded-md\"><button type=\"button\" style=\"width:33.33333333333333%;height:320px\" class=\"relative border-2 rounded-sm transition border-black bg-zinc-200\"><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 border-t border-zinc-500\" style=\"bottom:0px\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:20%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:40%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:60%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:80%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-y-2 left-1/2 border-l border-zinc-600\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1 right-1 border-t border-zinc-600\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-1 left-1 right-1 text-[10px] text-zinc-700\">2<!-- --> drawers</div></button><button type=\"button\" style=\"width:33.33333333333333%;height:320px\" class=\"relative border-2 rounded-sm transition border-zinc-500 bg-zinc-100 hover:bg-zinc-200\"><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 border-t border-zinc-500\" style=\"bottom:0px\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:20%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:40%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:60%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:80%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-y-2 left-1/2 border-l border-zinc-600\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1 right-1 border-t border-zinc-600\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-1 left-1 right-1 text-[10px] text-zinc-700\">2<!-- --> drawers</div></button><button type=\"button\" style=\"width:33.33333333333333%;height:320px\" class=\"relative border-2 rounded-sm transition border-zinc-500 bg-zinc-100 hover:bg-zinc-200\"><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 border-t border-zinc-500\" style=\"bottom:0px\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:20%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:40%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:60%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-1 border-t border-zinc-400\" style=\"top:80%\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-y-2 left-1/2 border-l border-zinc-600\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1 right-1 border-t border-zinc-600\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-1 left-1 right-1 text-[10px] text-zinc-700\">2<!-- --> drawers</div></button></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 mt-2 text-xs text-gray-600 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"px-2 py-1 border rounded bg-zinc-50\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Lane 1<!-- -->:</span> <!-- -->30<!-- -->W × <!-- -->84<!-- -->H × <!-- -->24<!-- -->D</div><div class=\"px-2 py-1 border rounded bg-zinc-50\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Lane 2<!-- -->:</span> <!-- -->30<!-- -->W × <!-- -->84<!-- -->H × <!-- -->24<!-- -->D</div><div class=\"px-2 py-1 border rounded bg-zinc-50\"><span class=\"font-semibold\">Lane 3<!-- -->:</span> <!-- -->30<!-- -->W × <!-- -->84<!-- -->H × <!-- -->24<!-- -->D</div></div></div></div></section></main><!-